2021年1月2日，在長達一個小時的電話會議中，時任[[美國總統|美國總統]][[唐納·川普|唐納·川普]]向[[佐治亞州|佐治亞州]]州務卿{{link-en|布拉德·拉芬斯佩格|Brad Raffensperger}}施加壓力，要求其更改[[2020年美國總統大選|2020年美國總統大選]]以來該州的選票總數。特朗普在大選中被[[喬·拜登|喬·拜登]]擊敗，但特朗普一直不承認選舉結果<ref name="AmySupervilleBrumback">{{cite web|url=https://apnews.com/article/election-2020-joe-biden-donald-trump-georgia-elections-a7b4aa4d8ce3bf52301ddbe620c6bff6|title=Trump, on tape, presses Ga. official to 'find' him votes|work=美聯社|first1=Jeff|last1=Amy|first2=Darlene|last2=Superville|first3=Kate|last3=Brumback|date=2021-01-04|accessdate=2021-01-04|archive-date=2021-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210104000015/https://apnews.com/article/election-2020-joe-biden-donald-trump-georgia-elections-a7b4aa4d8ce3bf52301ddbe620c6bff6}}</ref>，並與其支持者進行了各式各樣{{link-en|試圖推翻2020年美國總統選舉結果|Attempts to overturn the 2020 United States presidential election|試圖推翻大選結果}}的運動，例如提出超過80宗法律訴訟、呼籲支持者向國會議員施壓、向主持統計[[選舉人團|選舉人團]]票數的副總統[[邁克·彭斯|邁克·彭斯]]施壓等。在致電拉芬斯佩格之前，特朗普就已經反覆向至少三個他輸掉的[[搖擺州|搖擺州]]的官員要求重新點算各州的選民投票結果、將部分選民票作廢、或將在州選民投票中贏得投票權的[[民主黨_(美國)|民主黨]]選舉人替換成支持自己的[[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨]]選舉人。拉芬斯佩格在與特朗普通話的翌日將電話錄音提交給《[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]》報導並獲得其他媒體轉載<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/03/us/politics/trump-raffensperger-call-georgia.html|title=Trump, in Taped Call, Pressured Georgia Official to 'Find' Votes to Overturn Election|first1=Michael D.|last1=Shear|first2=Stephanie|last2=Saul|work=紐約時報|date=2021-01-03|accessdate=2021-01-04|archive-date=2021-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210104002713/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/03/us/politics/trump-raffensperger-call-georgia.html}}</ref><ref name="trump begs">{{cite web|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/donald-trump/trump-begs-georgia-secretary-state-overturn-election-results-remarkable-hourlong-n1252692|title=Trump begs Georgia secretary of state to overturn election results in remarkable hourlong phone call|work=NBC新聞|first1=Allan|last1=Smith|first2=Julia|last2=Jester|first3=Priscilla|last3=Thompson|date=2021-01-03|accessdate=2021-01-04|archive-date=2021-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210103234707/https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/donald-trump/trump-begs-georgia-secretary-state-overturn-election-results-remarkable-hourlong-n1252692}}</ref><ref name="trump demands">{{cite web|url=https://abcnews.go.com/Politics/trump-demands-georgia-secretary-state-find-votes-hand/story?id=75027350|title=Trump demands Georgia secretary of state 'find' enough votes to hand him win|work=ABC新聞|first=Quinn|last=Scanlon|date=2021-01-04|accessdate=2021-01-04|archive-date=2021-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210104020714/https://abcnews.go.com/Politics/trump-demands-georgia-secretary-state-find-votes-hand/story?id=75027350}}</ref>。

根據被公開的電話錄音，特朗普多次要求拉芬斯佩格「尋找11000張選票」，儘管拉芬斯佩格和他的法律顧問瑞安·爵曼尼（Ryan Germany）重複地指選舉並沒有任何舞弊跡象，並否定了特朗普提出諸如選票被篡改、扔掉、重複統計等的不實指控<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.npr.org/2021/01/03/953012128/this-was-a-scam-in-recorded-call-trump-pushed-official-to-overturn-georgia-vote|title='This Was A Scam': In Recorded Call, Trump Pushed Official To Overturn Georgia Vote|work=全國公共廣播電台|first=Stephen|last=Fowler|date=2021-01-03|accessdate=2021-01-04|archive-date=2021-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210103233114/https://www.npr.org/2021/01/03/953012128/this-was-a-scam-in-recorded-call-trump-pushed-official-to-overturn-georgia-vote}}</ref>。特朗普甚至指如果拉芬斯佩格和爵曼尼不按照他的意思指正選舉舞弊，「這對你和瑞安，你的律師，都是個重大危機<ref group=原文>特朗普：That's a big risk to you and to Ryan, your lawyer.</ref>」，其語氣被一些時事評論員和政治家認為是強人所難或具有威脅性，而法律專家則認為特朗普在這次電話對話中的言行有機會觸犯了州和聯邦法律<ref>多個來源：
