2021年1月11日，特朗普因为[[2021年美国国会大厦遭冲击事件|国会在統計選舉人團票時遭冲击]]而被[[美國眾議院|众议院]][[第二次特朗普弹劾案|第二次弹劾]]，這次電話事件亦被引用到彈劾議案中<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.bostonglobe.com/2021/01/11/nation/read-full-text-article-impeachment-filed-against-president-trump/ |title=Read the full text of the article of impeachment filed against President Trump |access-date=2021-01-11 |archive-date=2021-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114194029/https://www.bostonglobe.com/2021/01/11/nation/read-full-text-article-impeachment-filed-against-president-trump/}}</ref>。2021年2月，喬治亞州富爾頓縣地區檢察辦公室對這次事件連同更早前共和黨政要[[林賽·格雷厄姆|林賽·格雷厄姆]]致電拉芬斯佩格展開刑事調查。

==事件背景==
{{唐納·川普系列模板}}
在[[2020年美國總統選舉|2020年美國總統選舉]]中[[民主黨_(美國)|民主黨]]的候選人[[喬·拜登|喬·拜登]]擊敗了尋求連任、代表[[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨]]的[[唐納德·特朗普|唐納德·特朗普]]成為第46屆美國總統，其中在過往歷史上偏共和黨的[[喬治亞州|喬治亞州]]的選民投票中拜登以極為細微的得票比例差（11779票和0.24%之差），贏得這個州的16張[[選舉人團|選舉人團]]票，成為拜登贏得總統選舉的其中一個關鍵州。[[2020年唐纳德·特朗普竞选美国总统|特朗普的競選單位]]並不承認他落敗的[[搖擺州|搖擺州]]分的投票結果，並羅列出諸多選舉舞弊指控，這些指控都被查證者、選舉保安專家和法庭反駁或證偽，而特朗普和他的支持者所提出的所有{{link-en|針對2020年美國總統選舉的訴訟|Post-election lawsuits related to the 2020 United States presidential election|針對選舉的訴訟}}都沒有成功扭轉選舉結果，這些訴訟案中有一半是法庭不受理，其次是控方主動撤回訴訟<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.archives.gov/federal-register/electoral-college/allocation.html|title=Distribution of Electoral Votes|website=[[國家檔案和記錄管理局|國家檔案和記錄管理局]]|access-date=2019-01-03|archive-date=2019-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190109144218/https://www.archives.gov/federal-register/electoral-college/allocation.html}}</ref>。在兩位候選人得票非常接近的州分中在第一次點票後，又重新進行了手動點票，最終都是未能改變選舉結果<ref name=auditandrecount>{{cite news |first1=Lita Nadebah |last1=Beck |first2=John |last2=Fritze |first3=Kevin |last3=Johnson |first4=David |last4=Jackson |first5=Sean |last5=Rossman |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/elections/2020/11/18/election-2020-updates-joe-biden-donald-trump/6335864002/ |title=Election 2020 updates: Georgia nears recount completion; no more uncounted ballots found |work=[[今日美國|今日美國]] |date=2020-11-18 |accessdate=2020-11-19 |archive-date=2020-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201229144444/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/elections/2020/11/18/election-2020-updates-joe-biden-donald-trump/6335864002/ }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last1=Stirgus|first1=Eric|work=The Atlanta Journal-Constitution|title=Georgia election recount nears finish line with few hiccups|url=https://www.ajc.com/education/georgia-election-recount-nears-finish-line-with-few-hiccups/C57XUV33SVGQZBWGVXI5RVM65I/ |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203060439/https://www.ajc.com/education/georgia-election-recount-nears-finish-line-with-few-hiccups/C57XUV33SVGQZBWGVXI5RVM65I/ |archivedate=2020-12-03 |date=2020-11-16 |access-date=2020-11-16|language=en}}</ref>，拜登最終於2020年11月19日獲確認贏得喬治亞州<ref>{{cite news |first1=Jason |last1=Morris |first2=Maeve |last2=Reston |first3=Marshall |last3=Cohen |url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/11/19/politics/georgia-recount-election-results/index.html |title=Georgia confirms Biden victory and finds no widespread fraud after statewide audit |work=有線電視新聞網 |date=2020-11-19 |accessdate=2020-11-19 |archive-date=2020-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120004323/https://www.cnn.com/2020/11/19/politics/georgia-recount-election-results/index.html}}</ref>。

當2020年11月至12月的選舉訴訟案無法取得進展下，特朗普開始對至少[[密歇根州|密歇根州]]、[[賓夕法尼亞州|賓夕法尼亞州]]和喬治亞州這些他輸掉的州的共和黨地方或州官員親身或透過電話溝通，他向這些州的議員、州檢察長和州長施壓以求推翻選舉結果，包括要求他們重新點票、扔掉部分選票或將代表民主黨的選舉人團替換為共和黨的選舉人團<ref name="Gardner">{{cite news |last1=Gardner |first1=Amy |last2=Dawsey |first2=Josh |last3=Bade |first3=Rachael |title=Trump asks Pennsylvania House speaker for help overturning election results, personally intervening in a third state |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/trump-pennsylvania-speaker-call/2020/12/07/d65fe8c4-38bf-11eb-98c4-25dc9f4987e8_story.html |access-date=2020-12-15 |work=[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]] |date=2020-12-07 |archive-date=2020-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208020244/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/trump-pennsylvania-speaker-call/2020/12/07/d65fe8c4-38bf-11eb-98c4-25dc9f4987e8_story.html}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Kumar |first1=Anita |last2=Orr |first2=Gabby |last3=McGraw |first3=Meridith |title=Inside Trump's pressure campaign to overturn the election |url=https://www.politico.com/news/2020/12/21/trump-pressure-campaign-overturn-election-449486 |access-date=2020-12-22 |work=[[政客_(媒體)|政客]] |date=2020-12-21 |archive-date=2020-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201222010353/https://www.politico.com/news/2020/12/21/trump-pressure-campaign-overturn-election-449486}}</ref>。

12月5日有報導指特朗普致電了喬治亞州州長{{link-en|布萊恩·肯普|Brian Kemp}}，公開要求他和州務卿{{link-en|布拉德·拉芬斯佩格|Brad Raffensperger}}扭轉喬治亞州的選舉結果，並要挾如果不服從就會作出政治報復<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/trump-kemp-call-georgia/2020/12/05/fd8d677c-3721-11eb-8d38-6aea1adb3839_story.html |title=Trump calls Georgia governor to pressure him for help overturning Biden’s win in the state |last1=Gardner |first1=Amy |last2=Dawsey |first2=Josh |last3=Bade |first3=Rachael |date=2020-12-05 |work=華盛頓郵報 |accessdate=2021-01-11 |archive-date=2020-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205192533/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/trump-kemp-call-georgia/2020/12/05/fd8d677c-3721-11eb-8d38-6aea1adb3839_story.html }}</ref>。肯普和拉芬斯佩格都是共和黨黨員，但自從大選的選民投票結束後因為拒絕配合特朗普的舞弊指控，三者關係開始惡化。特朗普於12月30日在[[推特|推特]]發文指「肯普應該辭職，這個拒絕承認我們在喬治亞州獲得大勝的障礙物。<ref group=原文>特朗普：@BrainKempGA should resign from office. He is an obstructionist who refuses to admit that we won Georgia, BIG!</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.11alive.com/article/news/politics/trump-calls-on-georgia-gov-kemp-to-resign/85-f3d16351-b4bf-40ca-9581-5fc1b557d9e6|title=Trump calls Gov. Kemp 'obstructionist,' says he should resign|last=Raymond|first=Jonathan|date=2020-12-30|work=11Alive|accessdate=2021-01-03|archive-date=2021-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108015914/https://www.11alive.com/article/news/politics/trump-calls-on-georgia-gov-kemp-to-resign/85-f3d16351-b4bf-40ca-9581-5fc1b557d9e6}}</ref>」

===致電喬治亞州選舉調查主任===
《[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]》於2021年1月9日報導，特朗普在2020年12月23日致電了喬治亞州州務卿辦公室的選舉調查主任，當時這位匿名的選舉調查主任正在審計[[科布縣|科布縣]]的投票結果，這是應拉芬斯佩格要求調查州內選舉舞弊的指控。《華盛頓郵報》的此篇報導引述消息人士提供的訊息，聲稱特朗普對該選舉調查主任說如果她能找出舞弊行為就會成為一位「國家英雄」。於是有法律專家指特朗普的言語可能觸犯了行賄或妨礙選舉法。2020年12月29日，喬治亞州選舉調查團完成了審計並宣布所有針對喬治亞州的選舉舞弊指控都是子虛烏有，特朗普對調查結果表示不滿<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|last=Gardner|first=Amy|date=2021-01-09|title=‘Find the fraud’: Trump pressured a Georgia elections investigator in a separate call legal experts say could amount to obstruction|work=華盛頓郵報|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/trump-call-georgia-investigator/2021/01/09/7a55c7fa-51cf-11eb-83e3-322644d82356_story.html|access-date=2021-01-09|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114194053/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/trump-call-georgia-investigator/2021/01/09/7a55c7fa-51cf-11eb-83e3-322644d82356_story.html}}</ref>。2021年1月4日，拉芬斯佩格在《[[早安美國|早安美國]]》的新聞訪問中確認了這次通話內容<ref>{{Cite web|last=Scanlan|first=Quinn|date=2021-01-04|title=Trump 'just plain wrong' on fraud claims: Georgia Secretary of State Raffensperger|url=https://www.goodmorningamerica.com/news/story/trump-plain-wrong-fraud-claims-georgia-secretary-state-75032595|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114194043/https://www.goodmorningamerica.com/news/story/trump-plain-wrong-fraud-claims-georgia-secretary-state-75032595|archive-date=2021-01-14|access-date=2021-01-10|website=Good Morning America|language=en}}</ref>，《華盛頓郵報》出於保護事件主角的安全而沒有公開該選舉調查主任的身份<ref name=":0" />。

然而，根據拉芬斯伯格在事發兩個月後公佈的川普與該選舉調查主任的通話錄音，川普並未要求對方找出舞弊行為以及說對方能因此成為「國家英雄」。《華盛頓郵報》於2021年3月11日承認其於1月9日的報導是錯誤的，並更正了報導的標題和內文<ref>{{cite news | title = 《華郵》認錯！更正抹黑川普報導 修改標題內文 | url = https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3468039 | newspaper = [[自由時報|自由時報]] | date = 2021年3月16日 | accessdate = 2021年3月17日 | archive-date = 2021年3月16日 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210316235030/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3468039 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

==致電喬治亞州州務卿拉芬斯佩格==
2021年1月2日，特朗普與喬治亞州州務卿拉芬斯佩格舉行了長達1小時的閉門電話會議<ref name="trump begs" /><ref name="CNN-20210103">{{cite news |last1=Duster |first1=Chandelis |last2=Cole |first2=Devan |title=In call, Trump demands Georgia officials 'find' votes to tilt election |url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/03/politics/donald-trump-brad-raffensperger-call-washington-post/index.html |date=2021-01-03 |work=[[有線電視新聞網|有線電視新聞網]] |accessdate=2021-01-03 |archive-date=2021-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210103193418/https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/03/politics/donald-trump-brad-raffensperger-call-washington-post/index.html }}</ref>。陪同特朗普一邊的有白宮幕僚長[[馬克·米道斯|馬克·米道斯]]、貿易顧問[[彼得·納瓦羅|彼得·納瓦羅]]、司法部官員{{link-en|約翰·洛特|John Lott}}、法律系教授{{link-en|約翰·伊斯特曼|John C. Eastman}}和律師[[魯迪·朱利安尼|魯迪·朱利安尼]]、{{link-en|克萊塔·米切爾|Cleta Mitchell}}等人，拉芬斯佩格則由他的法律顧問瑞安·爵曼尼陪同參與對話<ref name="postobtained">{{cite web |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/trump-raffensperger-call-transcript-georgia-vote/2021/01/03/2768e0cc-4ddd-11eb-83e3-322644d82356_story.html |first=Amy |last=Gardener |first2=Paulina |last2=Firozi |title=The Post has published Trump's full phone call with Georgia election officials. Listen to the audio and read the transcript. |website=[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]] |date=2021-01-03 |accessdate=2021-01-03 |archive-date=2021-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210103213550/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/trump-raffensperger-call-transcript-georgia-vote/2021/01/03/2768e0cc-4ddd-11eb-83e3-322644d82356_story.html}}</ref>。翌日1月3日，《[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]》和其他主流媒體獲得了這次會議的錄音<ref name="postobtained" /><ref name="18calls">{{cite news|url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/04/politics/trump-brad-raffensperger-calls-georgia/index.html|title=There were 18 attempted calls from the White House to GA secretary of state's office, sources say|date=2021-01-04|work=有線電視新聞網|accessdate=2021-01-11|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114194041/https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/04/politics/trump-brad-raffensperger-calls-georgia/index.html}}</ref>。

===會議內容被公開===
1月3日，特朗普在錄音被媒體公開前發推文指與拉芬斯佩格進行了電話會議，稱對方無意或無能力證明選舉舞弊<ref group=原文>特朗普：I spoke to Secretary of State Brad Raffensperger yesterday about Fulton County and voter fraud in Georgia. He was unwilling, or unable, to answer questions such as the “ballots under table” scam, ballot destruction, out of state “voters”, dead voters, and more. He has no clue!</ref><ref name="He has no clue">{{cite news|url=https://www.11alive.com/article/news/politics/elections/trump-tweets-about-fulton-county-brad-raffensperger-brian-kemp/85-a503efec-df8a-42ee-a92f-70271eac840f|title=Trump asks Georgia election officials to 'find' votes during call with Sec. of State|last=Braverman|first=Jason|date=2021-01-03|work=11Alive|accessdate=2021-01-11|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114194041/https://www.11alive.com/article/news/politics/elections/trump-tweets-about-fulton-county-brad-raffensperger-brian-kemp/85-a503efec-df8a-42ee-a92f-70271eac840f}}</ref>。拉芬斯佩格指自己本來不打算公開談論事件，但當看到特朗普的推文對自己進行不實攻擊後認為有必要出面澄清，他指1月2日的電話會議是當天臨急舉行的，因為特朗普在當天早上看到自己在[[福斯新聞|福斯新聞]]上回應指「大選結果公正和特朗普已經落敗」<ref name = Buchanan>{{cite news|url=https://www.11alive.com/article/news/politics/elections/brad-raffensperger-speaks/85-bdbe200f-4c60-48cc-af42-b8b70ad13f65|title=Secretary of State Brad Raffensperger opens up about Trump phone call|last=Buchanan|first=Christopher|date=2021-01-04|work=11Alive|accessdate=2021-01-11|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114194033/https://www.11alive.com/article/news/politics/elections/brad-raffensperger-speaks/85-bdbe200f-4c60-48cc-af42-b8b70ad13f65}}</ref>。後來有消息指於1月2日前的一週之間，特朗普有18次嘗試過與拉芬斯佩格通電，但基於特朗普和他的團隊正在對喬治亞州州務卿和州長提出多項訴訟，拉芬斯佩格決定迴避這種會談<ref name="18calls"/>。

